<p>The Centre for Soldiers Wives &amp; Mothers<br/>92B Pitt St. Sydney<br/>4-1-16</p>
<p>Dear Mr. Layton &ndash;<br/>We are sending Mrs. Lehair who has had some assistance from you before.</p>
<p>She has one debt &pound;3-15-0 to the Bon Marche which she seems unable to meet otherwise she can get on alright on the military pay.</p>
<p>She has three young children &amp; is paying 12/- per week for rent of room &ndash;</p>
<p>Perhaps you may be able to help &ndash;</p>
<p>Yours truly<br/>B. Booth.</p>
